As a sales representative, I respond to customers queries, guide and provide training to new joiners for effective customer service. Manage cash register, POS, handling calls, reaching the KPI's. With this job, I developed interpersonal skills, patience, and empathy. Hope to see you next time in the Myer Sydney City.
